# Ops runbook — Smart Purge for Breeze Cache

## Repos and lanes

- **Canonical repo:** `PixelParade/breeze-smart-purge-plugin` at `breeze-smart-purge-plugin/`.
- **Staging:** `breeze-smart-purge.pixelparade.dev` — verify hostname before remote changes.
- **Three lanes:** `main` → staging CI (agency tree); tag `v*` → agency zip → MainWP clients; wporg zip → SVN for external users. See `docs/MAINWP_ROLLOUT.md` and `docs/WPORG_SUBMISSION.md`.
- **MainWP clients:** agency build only — `BSP_GITHUB_TOKEN`, never wordpress.org install for this plugin.

## Staging verification (pre-approved for agents)

Read-only checks on `breeze-smart-purge.pixelparade.dev` (WP-CLI, Novamira, Cloudways cache purge, browser snapshot) are auto-allowed — see `docs/ACCESS.md`. Never echo passwords or API keys in output.

